quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,"Our Lord, we believed with what You descended, and we followed the messenger, so write (include) us with the witnessing/testifying"
  3,54,"And they cheated/deceived and God cheated/deceived, and God (is) the best (of) the cheaters/deceivers"
  3,55,"When God said: \"You Jesus I am, I am making you die and raising you to Me and purifying you from those who disbelieved, and making those who followed you above those who disbelieved to the Resurrection Day, then to Me (is) your return, so I judge/rule between you in what, you were in it differing"
  3,56,"So but those who disbelieved, so I torture them, a strong (severe) torture in the present world/near and the end (other life), and (there are) nothing for them from victoriors/saviors"
  3,57,"And but those who believed and did the correct/righteous deeds, so He fulfills/completes (to) them their rewards , and God does not love/like the unjust/oppressive"
  3,58,"That We read/recited it on you from the signs/verses/evidences and the reminder, the wise/judicious"
  3,59,"That Jesus` example at God (is) as Adam`s example, (He) created him from dust/earth then He said to him: \"Be.\" So he became"
  3,60,"The truth (is) from your Lord, so do not be from the doubting/arguing"
  3,61,"So who argued/quarreled with you in it from after what came to you from the knowledge, so say: \"Come, we (will) call our sons, and your sons, and our women, and your women, and ourselves and yourselves, then we curse each other/pray humbly , so we make God`s curse/torture on the liars"